sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Route53 as Route53 DNS<br/>(Optional)
    participant APIGW as API Gateway<br/>HTTP API
    participant LambdaAPI as Lambda<br/>API Server
    participant DynamoDB as DynamoDB<br/>Tables
    participant SQS as SQS Queue
    participant LambdaWorker as Lambda<br/>Worker

    User->>Route53: HTTPS Request<br/>(api.dev.example.com)
    Route53->>APIGW: DNS Resolution
    User->>APIGW: HTTPS Request<br/>(Default Endpoint)
    APIGW->>LambdaAPI: Invoke Function<br/>(GET/POST /users, /events)
    LambdaAPI->>DynamoDB: Read/Write Data
    DynamoDB-->>LambdaAPI: Data Response
    LambdaAPI->>SQS: Send Message<br/>(Async Processing)
    LambdaAPI-->>APIGW: HTTP Response
    APIGW-->>User: JSON Response

    SQS->>LambdaWorker: Event Source Mapping<br/>(Trigger)
    LambdaWorker->>DynamoDB: Process & Update Data
    DynamoDB-->>LambdaWorker: Confirmation
    LambdaWorker-->>SQS: Message Processed
